<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html ng-app="Redwood">

		<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ STATIC_URL }}framework/js/redwoodAdmin.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="{{ STATIC_URL }}ExperimentComponents/js/payoutSelector.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="{{ STATIC_URL }}experiments/redwood-portfolio-allocation/admin.js"></script>
